The other two show dogs on four stolen from the outside of a motel in Bellflower have been found, Los Angeles County Sheriffs announced Thursday.
The four show dogs - two Akitas and two Welsh Pembroke Corgis - disappeared Tuesday when someone stole the Chevrolet Express van in which they had spent the night outside a Bellflower Motel 6, authorities said.
