Animators should present solid rather than misleading information.
Regarding suicide, the host Stéphane Dupont had considered that suicide is a cowardly gesture.
The majority of Committee members concluded that the message was that suicide should not be seen as a solution to life's problems.
"The majority of the Committee considers that the episodes in question of 'Dupont le Midi' have addressed a sensitive subject in a fair and appropriate manner."
