The veil lifted on a complex Canada...
The new U.S. diplomatic cables leaked by WikiLeaks lift the veil on what the U.S. considers the Canadians’ inferiority complex to the Americans, but they also betray the latter’s sense of superiority to Canada.
Thus, U.S. diplomats are astonished that every Canadian voter does not have Canadian-U.S. relations in mind when going to vote and believe that President Obama's visit helped the Conservative government pass its budget in 2009!
